title: books on infrared and raman spectroscopy
description:
Four books on Raman and IR spectroscopy :

Infrared and Raman spectroscopy, methods and applications (VCH)
The Raman Effect: A unified Treatment of the Theory of Raman Scattering by Molecules, D. A. Long (John Wileys and Sons)
Molecular Light Scattering and Optical Activity, Laurence Barron (Cambridge, 2nd edition)
Modern Spectroscopy, J. Michael Hollas (Wiley, 4th edition)
